### Manali Hotel & Package Management API
### Sample API Calls for Testing

# Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@adminToken = {{admin_login_response.response.body.access_token}}

### 1. User Registration (Local)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "John Doe"
}

### 2. Admin Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@manali.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 3. User Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 4. Google OAuth (Open in browser)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/google

### 5. Get Current User Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

