### 8. Get All Hotels with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/hotels?page=1&limit=10&city=Manali&type=luxury&minPrice=3000&maxPrice=9000&rating=4

### 9. Get Single Hotel
GET {{baseUrl}}/hotels/{{hotel_id}}

### 10. Create Hotel Schedule
POST {{baseUrl}}/hotels/{{hotel_id}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2024-12-25",
  "availableRooms": 10,
  "specialPrice": 9000,
  "status": "available",
  "notes": "Christmas special pricing"
}

