### 13. Get All Packages with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/packages?page=1&limit=10&type=adventure&minPrice=10000&maxPrice=25000&duration=5&destination=Manali

### 14. Get Featured Packages
GET {{baseUrl}}/packages/featured?limit=4

### 15. Create Package Schedule
POST {{baseUrl}}/packages/{{package_id}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2024-12-20",
  "endDate": "2024-12-24",
  "availableSlots": 12,
  "specialPrice": 20000,
  "status": "available",
  "notes": "Christmas special batch with additional bonfire night",
  "pickupLocation": "Mall Road Bus Stand, Manali",
  "pickupTime": "08:00:00"
}

### 16. Get Hotel Schedules
GET {{baseUrl}}/hotels/{{hotel_id}}/schedules?startDate=2024-12-01&endDate=2024-12-31

### 17. Get Package Schedules  
GET {{baseUrl}}/packages/{{package_id}}/schedules?startDate=2024-12-01&endDate=2024-12-31

### 18. Search Available Hotels
GET {{baseUrl}}/hotels/available/search?checkIn=2024-12-25&checkOut=2024-12-28

### 19. Search Available Packages
GET {{baseUrl}}/packages/available/search?startDate=2024-12-25&endDate=2024-12-28

### 20. Update Hotel (Admin/Owner only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/hotels/{{hotel_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pricePerNight": 6000,
  "amenities": ["WiFi", "Swimming Pool", "Spa", "Restaurant", "Room Service", "Gym", "Parking", "Conference Hall"]
}

### 21. Update Package (Admin/Owner only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/packages/{{package_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 19500,
  "maxGroupSize": 18
}

### 22. Delete Hotel (Admin/Owner only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/hotels/{{hotel_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 23. Delete Package (Admin/Owner only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/packages/{{package_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 24. Get All Users (Admin only - if endpoint exists)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}